thread.title_full: GO Rentals New Zealand reviewed by Ray Olsen

author: Ray Olsen
title: Ray Olsen
text: Awesome experience with go rentals,very friendly staff easy to arrange a vehicle . The vehicle was top of the line and such a breeze to drive . I will be renting again and no problems recommending to others . I highly recommend this company for a no fuss experience
